								</g>
							</svg>
						</div>

						<div class="tracking-tight text-[#7E71A3]">
							<p class="text-sm font-semibold">Quieres salvar la relación</p>
							<p class="text-xs">Si deseas sanar el vínculo de pareja y recuperar a tu familia</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div
						class="mx-auto flex w-[85%] items-center space-x-4 rounded-full bg-[#f3f3f3] px-4 py-1 shadow-lg lg:w-[40%]"
					>
						<div class="flex w-[48px] flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center">
							<svg
								width="43"
								height="40"
								viewBox="0 0 43 40"
								fill="none"
								xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
								class="h-[40px] w-[43px]"
							>
								<mask
									id="mask0_2009_5092"
									style="mask-type:luminance"
									maskUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
